{"tid":1086180,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[內蒙古遊記]我在草原馳騁的日子 (多圖+你問我盡答)","createTime":"2019-03-31T16:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T23:35:54.000Z","uid":241103,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7213946be9ebeb0328b4e6a3ff8581e58c516e","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"作為一個城市人，而且生活係香港，山同海對我地黎講，一啲都唔會陌生，但一望無際嘅大草原，往往只能夠係電視電影入面先睇到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbBkQz6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbBkQz6.jpg&h=11790c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗一完我嘅草原夢，我係2018年嘅9月3號同另外三個朋友一齊飛咗去內蒙古呼倫貝爾，展開咗為期8日嘅草原之行<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxDGz1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxDGz1k.jpg&h=c69055ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呢次旅程中，我地試過係草原放風箏，餵羊揸牛奶，策馬奔騰，揸越野卡丁車，參篝火會，睇星但天氣差睇唔到，比司機水，坐快艇去中俄邊界，睇俄妹鋼管舞等等，好多嘅第一次，好多嘅難忘回憶<br />\n<br />\n由於內蒙古人口比較少，去嘅時侯又過咗暑假高峰期，曾經考慮過旅行車自駕遊，但由於唔熟當地，加上我地當中只有一個人有大陸車牌，所以最後選擇係透過攜程嘅微領隊幫我地規劃大概嘅行程，同安排司機<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我地嘅行程，但去到根據天氣同司機嘅建議有些少唔同，但好多景點嘅名唔多記得，名好難記<br />\n<br />\n9日3日 接機入住<br />\n<br />\n9月4日 海拉爾 -金賬汗草原 - 莫日格勒河 -額爾古納<br />\n<br />\n9月5日 額爾古納 - 電塔山 - 白樺林 - 恩河 - 室韋（木刻楞酒店）<br />\n<br />\n9月6日 室韋 - 蒙古之源 - 俄羅斯邊界線 - 烏蘭山 - 八卦河 - 黑山頭日落山（草原騎馬，卡丁車，射箭，烤全羊，篝火晚會)<br />\n<br />\n9月7日 黑山頭 - 186彩帶河 - 呼倫湖 - 滿洲里國門 - 套娃廣場<br />\n<br />\n9月8日 滿洲里  - 玫瑰峰 - 伊爾斯 - 阿爾山園子天池小鎮<br />\n<br />\n9月9日 阿爾山(天池山，三潭峽，杜鵑湖，地池，鹿鳴湖，石塘林）<br />\n<br />\n9月8日 阿爾山 - 海拉爾 - 紅花爾基 - 伊敏 - 海拉爾結束<br />\n<br />\n去內蒙古最太嘅洗費都係機票，頂早買太約2千幾3千，我地同另外二個fd係6月到就訂咗深圳直飛，但另一個fd遲我地半個月定一個月買同一班機就貴成千，所以改買轉機但平啲嘅票 (香港好似冇直飛，要北京轉，而且選擇太少同時間麻麻)<br />\n<br />\n全程直飛都要成6個半鐘，我地9點3機，去到都下午4點<br />\n<br />\n而包車嘅費用係800人仔一日，我地為咗坐得舒服啲揀咗坐7人車，事後我地覺得呢個係明志嘅選擇，但遇上司機雷哥就係我地最唔想嘅事<br />\n<br />\n先附上啲味精色風影相先，之後會嘅相就唔會有味精<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGR5hfo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGR5hfo.jpg&h=0803a4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrJ3Om4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrJ3Om4.jpg&h=9eabd485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZLeaAq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZLeaAq.jpg&h=e0377774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98Lmz16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98Lmz16.jpg&h=38ee8b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpnoOm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpnoOm7.jpg&h=9bb78a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HV2oOm8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHV2oOm8.jpg&h=21ba0dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4RH3Vu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4RH3Vu.jpg&h=91bf3c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSb8ZtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSb8ZtQ.jpg&h=6f0da1f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7af85738539ba0c6dc6ea2be8bd90f5908aa714","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85b80eb3c5363a2f4f9a43281e409eee48f48dc4","tid":1086180,"uid":37901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"支持下先!"},{"pid":"b781cb97b7d9f75ee85e4ab1519d86e0294e9631","tid":1086180,"uid":147580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5e859aca7037ba1feb8785911e19bb9ceafbe0","tid":1086180,"uid":28426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:16:21.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885b2858beaa76dac2d1dd5fed61d00e8dc48e28","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"手殘出多咗兩個Post 呢個先係正常"},{"pid":"d9d05243fff76c7bb96b2001388afa2030d0b2f6","tid":1086180,"uid":124499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"我上年都去左， 但冇去咁多日， 由海拉爾出發去滿洲里再返轉頭"},{"pid":"4ff861d8e804cec980184908f4927c0f0710da5c","tid":1086180,"uid":55923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"石屎蒙古包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0eab74c7100296b3728d3b7937b4a1e5c6d579","tid":1086180,"uid":160579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇騎馬嗰part"},{"pid":"c7e61b94b15471929533a8a17be0fbc5a252954f","tid":1086180,"uid":172694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔去蒙古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4bef1606ecbb72019c64a4b40892cea184e859","tid":1086180,"uid":14255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d99e4ec32a09d940fd66cbeed7c91d59a79df9a3","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"第二日我地先去食過早餐，食嘅野幾正常，而且唔算難食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8j27To.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8j27To.jpg&h=cfcb6a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ido3Sj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fido3Sj4.jpg&h=c8d8c1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就正式出發去景點，呢個景點你當係一個公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XuSXbDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuSXbDH.jpg&h=c3bb4567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3j3LkxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3j3LkxB.jpg&h=00845dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3PZp0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3PZp0H.jpg&h=b251dbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始放風箏，隻風箏試過跌落過幾次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJeOijx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJeOijx.jpg&h=cb4749f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWhPNoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWhPNoX.jpg&h=802d3af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩咗冇耐之後，出發去下一個景點，一個牧場咁嘅野，有羊餵有牛奶揸有箭射有衫換<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jWXWjb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jWXWjb.gif&h=b4cc9205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjHL5cR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjHL5cR.jpg&h=cd1c68cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmrMPWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmrMPWR.jpg&h=ce6c8a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbtCWBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbtCWBU.jpg&h=10a144bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrjZqvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrjZqvf.jpg&h=293468dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以坐拖拉機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbtWsJN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbtWsJN.gif&h=f4db659f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9Hszpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9Hszpf.jpg&h=ed7d0473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係嗰到玩咗成個下午，之後就去咗食晚飯，食烤羊，本身叫咗羊扒，但司機雷哥話隔離枱個司機佢識(另一個司機+司機條女)，話佢地點咗羊腿，不如合埋一張枱食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHqqk7W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHqqk7W.gif&h=130a5b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkAxLzK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkAxLzK.gif&h=0f5a5bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食嘅時侯老闆為我地高歌一曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，認住右下角呢個係司機雷哥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkOO3oy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkOO3oy.gif&h=8b7fdb75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完正當話比錢，個兩條友(司機+司機條女)，完全冇比，仲走撚左，人都走撚走，加上我地唔係地頭蟲，就算，當請佢地<br />\n<br />\n之後返酒店，結束第二日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8dSLD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8dSLD3.jpg&h=3eca2d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最搞笑係另一間房有麻雀枱，仲要係電動，我地打咗陣牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UegQxjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUegQxjs.jpg&h=0e3ca723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"015196db1d1efdf0171f7345d5da226202907453","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7e61b94b15471929533a8a17be0fbc5a252954f","tid":1086180,"uid":172694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔去蒙古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"內蒙方便啲，語言通，蒙古下次再去"},{"pid":"00a8e7aadfd504340abdcf2e5616c055633dcdd5","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ff861d8e804cec980184908f4927c0f0710da5c","tid":1086180,"uid":55923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"石屎蒙古包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"全部都係咁濟，真係好荒蕪嘅地方先見到原始嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d03ae338e72b0b8090cf4cf8dfe9530f965e3fd","tid":1086180,"uid":84223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"做乜自爆?"},{"pid":"feff57c0422556d8748d8e9f90de5f71633cc716","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d03ae338e72b0b8090cf4cf8dfe9530f965e3fd","tid":1086180,"uid":84223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"做乜自爆?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"一時大意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f80140e6d0be00ec08d42d7cad3b6da0eccadfa","tid":1086180,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"成個行程洗費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28278bef5ceea8a234dc3f67501d6d13031f4126","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:45:54.000Z","msg":"內蒙暑假去先靚喔<br />\n<br />\n不過毒撚去就大撚獲，唔包車＝玩唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n阿爾山個火車站最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7448055e394cc358942f17a915114090a70927a2","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"９點３機<br />\n你們前一晚到深圳定點上去?"},{"pid":"738cd773dd3099311192254c03c11243d0834a27","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"第三日朝早無記錯係去咗呢間俄羅斯人屋企，無錯，呢個係一個景點，按一頭收費，吃下野聽佢想當年，之後玩下遊戲，不過啲野好難食，我認為係一個伏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LESDPNV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLESDPNV.gif&h=e6fb37f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzEZze1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzEZze1.gif&h=0d363a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TANH8q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TANH8q.jpg&h=05107aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後下午去咗個森林公園，睇下白樺林同動物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEkxUfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEkxUfL.jpg&h=69e996d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYssH87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYssH87.jpg&h=45e14367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HcsH9o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HcsH9o.jpg&h=1487a55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LopZzgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLopZzgq.jpg&h=10b9b109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RyEuWuO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyEuWuO.jpg&h=984e383f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到啲鹿同唔知狐狸定咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gmv6ehd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmv6ehd.gif&h=debb3503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4JogvA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4JogvA.gif&h=c001ba50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqmX5o0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqmX5o0.gif&h=9f1bfcbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到咁上下，見到個好靚嘅景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2uKLpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2uKLpw.jpg&h=eeede228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YncUip.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YncUip.gif&h=96fe869c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VX4Lqt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VX4Lqt.gif&h=e40c3c00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩到差唔多，我地就去入住同上一日差唔多嘅酒店，夜晚雷哥帶我地去食燒烤，啲牛羊肉真係好食過平時係香港食嘅好多，到目前為止，我地仍然覺得佢係好人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rUd300Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrUd300Z.jpg&h=52e290dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crySUmF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrySUmF.gif&h=5324b678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後果日我地會騎馬入住蒙古包"},{"pid":"9127101e004878938c6fd82891cd4661bd05a14c","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7448055e394cc358942f17a915114090a70927a2","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"９點３機<br />\n你們前一晚到深圳定點上去?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"唔係，4點幾5點係香港坐直通車上去"},{"pid":"5b7b636e7b959a327612937dea5c8a9a646771cc","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28278bef5ceea8a234dc3f67501d6d13031f4126","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:45:54.000Z","msg":"內蒙暑假去先靚喔<br />\n<br />\n不過毒撚去就大撚獲，唔包車＝玩唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n阿爾山個火車站最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"暑假唔多旅行團咩，最怕旺季去旅行<br />\n<br />\n唔唔時間睇嘅景唔同"},{"pid":"b11429a5c05fb931be5ca485676440ea3c492356","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f80140e6d0be00ec08d42d7cad3b6da0eccadfa","tid":1086180,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"成個行程洗費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"我好似用咗7千右右"},{"pid":"4b030cb8964a73a135122f9f203413b2507466f9","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9127101e004878938c6fd82891cd4661bd05a14c","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7448055e394cc358942f17a915114090a70927a2","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"９點３機<br />\n你們前一晚到深圳定點上去?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"唔係，4點幾5點係香港坐直通車上去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"環島定永東<br />\n駛唔駛$100"},{"pid":"ebad5d0942f3dc02ec91d35f718e6c46b37c7b55","tid":1086180,"uid":219420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"留名睇雷哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff9130171c6bc143d9d4966165e62e5051477a9","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"第四日朝早求其食咗個面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CF5NJks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCF5NJks.jpg&h=08cb451a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就出去黑山頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMJrYUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMJrYUh.jpg&h=89bbbe2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXy31ir.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXy31ir.gif&h=f08bc3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRpCmit.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRpCmit.gif&h=7d1dfffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雷哥帶咗我地去一間馬場，話呢場有護具有保險所以貴啲，每人五舊水，包草原大穿越同玩一圈越野卡丁車，當時覺得有啲貴，但都黎到冇理由唔玩，加上雷哥一直都表現得老實，所以就比咗錢<br />\n<br />\n第一次騎馬，覺得幾特別，不過覺得齋漫步好無聊，想試下跑，可惜個plan唔包，卡丁車都唔错<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vmX5D2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vmX5D2.gif&h=ae682dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AHkiZ3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AHkiZ3.gif&h=dda1a6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住車咗我地去一座唔知咩山，話風景幾好，但七人車只能去到山腳，叫我地自己行上去，佢係下面等我地<br />\n<br />\n見到有個摩托車阿姨，佢話10蚊雞一轉，我地好落意咁比咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rfFi3v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rfFi3v.gif&h=d7a8f723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面係幾正，係頂可以見到四面都係一馬平川嘅草原，仲見到有牧半人放羊，漫山遍野都係羊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hp6Ze7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hp6Ze7.jpg&h=606bfee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tetSUOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtetSUOk.jpg&h=a026dd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8jKLKs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8jKLKs.gif&h=4594d87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後雷哥車咗我地去今晚住嘅蒙古大營-弘吉剌部<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkqFi6h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkqFi6h.gif&h=cdfcd0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCozoHX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCozoHX.gif&h=cbe5cead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係果到週圍行，個fd係主帳個大廳見到個練緊結他嘅女仔，我地就慫恿佢彈返首<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9Xz7ZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9Xz7ZY.jpg&h=8c87b734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來我地識咗嗰個女仔，佢係今晚晚會嘅其中一個表演者，傾傾下發現原來呢地騎馬好平，佢話我地比人水咗，跟我帶咗我地去呢個大營旁邊嘅馬場<br />\n<br />\n由於佢識馬場山老闆娘，仲可以平啲，我屌吖，40蚊就有個哥仔帶你騎住跑一圈，玩卡丁車都係。我地當時心諗，雷哥，仆你個街吖<br />\n<br />\n之後我揀咗快跑一圈，佢地玩卡丁車/慢跑，冇帶護具冇保險，但個價我不能抗拒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Hf9WXV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Hf9WXV.jpg&h=8ca58ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未試過都唔知，策馬奔騰係咁刺激，帶我騎嘅哥仔話頂唔順就喊停，先慢行，急步行，再奔跑，原來騎馬急步行係好唔舒服，起伏好急，反而跑起上來好穩定起伏好爽，當然我都有一兩次差啲甩手叫停咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試到騎馬嘅快感，亦都愛上咗，如果播埋動力火車首 當就perfect 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efdWB1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefdWB1v.jpg&h=403d54d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r887JGY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr887JGY.gif&h=00617315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騎咗幾圈，已經日落<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GXEiQnp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXEiQnp.jpg&h=cf3d4378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我地返去參加篝火晚會，食野唱歌跳舞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hzPe79P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhzPe79P.gif&h=4320c255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9ccUPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9ccUPQ.jpg&h=9af8a978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2g2TEgB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2g2TEgB.gif&h=1e088aab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係接近完美嘅一天，除咗被雷哥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de8cd3c4e9d0cbcf9cc13390dc6b41033e179f8","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b030cb8964a73a135122f9f203413b2507466f9","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9127101e004878938c6fd82891cd4661bd05a14c","tid":1086180,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7448055e394cc358942f17a915114090a70927a2","tid":1086180,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"９點３機<br />\n你們前一晚到深圳定點上去?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"唔係，4點幾5點係香港坐直通車上去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"環島定永東<br />\n駛唔駛$100"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"永東 唔記得價"},{"pid":"0977ec5716ae167acbf3e1e67e6d8b9ee6bf4df7","tid":1086180,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9aec023eb2986249574ba9dcdd8b49e4ed255010","tid":1086180,"uid":28426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:36:26.000Z","msg":"繼續G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4076c190864d01d3535525889b4753e6ae52a25","tid":1086180,"uid":35240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d2f09387c7db6bfd5c63163335a0174795965b","tid":1086180,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d5c2923ef78a875e7c2915fcde26826c2d46bb","tid":1086180,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336ce5e1363e25d8290734115c778639a019a61c","tid":1086180,"uid":68604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"我之前去內蒙又係俾司機呃<br />\n又係俾人呃左都唔知 係當地人同番我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e30a5d71fb0a4802ca8131d27f3c9525540121","tid":1086180,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ca7868ff8d1f2217eda2531bbed8302e1fbcfe","tid":1086180,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c45ace4a9ae7f751e0926b14a11360a1acbac0","t